@baseUrl = http://localhost:5180

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# POWER
# State transitions:  Offline → Idle (power on)
#                     Idle / Charging → Offline (power off)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Power On
# Transitions drone: Offline → Idle
POST {{baseUrl}}/drone/power/on

###

### Power Off
# Transitions drone: Idle or Charging → Offline
POST {{baseUrl}}/drone/power/off

###
